msgid "Sender email address"
msgstr "Dirección de correo del remitente"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:920
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Dedicated From: address for admission, vote, welcome, departure, invitation, "
"and submission-review emails — e.g. hello@agnosis.art. Deliberately separate "
"from the Settings → Newsletter sender: these are one-off actions (a vote "
